Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介回來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一刻終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打了 別打了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停 暫…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為恭介他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 是理樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我昨晚通宵了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介不在時他們倆一直忍著沒打架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為你在就能隨時過去調解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我來定個規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙方都空手的話 真人優勢太大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對的 都拿著竹刀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾優勢又太大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們隨手扔點武器給他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越沒用的東西越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倆抓到什麼就用什麼做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為全是沒有實用性的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,較之現在這種狀態就安全多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥 開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香蕉?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你捧著隻貓幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的武器 有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說用這玩意怎麼打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等的鈴大人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准欺負弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者? 是說你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的是這隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你們打架的理由是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙編了「茅廁頓開」這詞來坑我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜其所賜 今天我和人家交談時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不經意間說了「真是茅廁頓開啊」用到了這個錯詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這理由也太渺小了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你主動跑來問我「茅廁頓開」的意思的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你說的是茅塞頓開這詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就回答了你這詞是指突然理解了某一事態而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就交代清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茅廁頓開是啥意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 這下你知道責任在哪邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 你想逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用貓爪撕裂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你是恭介的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍觀的 扔點武器過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鰻…鰻魚派…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原君 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不僅限於今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是自童年相識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他們玩成一片時起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不斷重複著的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那最痛苦的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我失去雙親後沒多久的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自閉的我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們四個出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強敵出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝 理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們上 理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你們是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懲治罪惡的正義夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人稱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那的確是個強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進行了英勇奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人 我們不會忘記你的犧牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒拜託你們這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我們的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也是熱鬧日子的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣和他們度過一段時光後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知不覺間忘記了心中的痛楚和寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的內心被快樂充實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終開始祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的時光能永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 今天慘透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不叫小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是新來的還沒名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫列儂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列儂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你取名字總是這麼隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛因斯坦 蓋茨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧德麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說恭介 這次你去哪兒應聘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社 東京的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走路去東京!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢啊 我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們明年也三年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對也會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反正是不會徒步去求職的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 的確如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年後我們不是在準備升學考試就是在求職了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止都在一起的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業後也可能各奔東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能說的是 一年後恭介肯定不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才懶得去想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼遙遠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在這個狀態能一直持續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 像過去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想啊 上小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們為了找尋罪惡走遍了很多地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我和你們混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介一直是我們的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他帶領我們做出那些激動人心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做只有現在才能做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組個棒球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊名就叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那兒 你就站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 你當投手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說說這麼分配的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這樣從發展角度來看會更熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼的發展?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們Little Busters隊的比賽必須感人且具有戲劇性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成是受漫畫影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹 你去當接球手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 值得紀念的第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開球儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我扔…這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 全力扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 我直說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賜予你「神級零控」稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,434)\fs21}No Control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴得到了「神級零控」稱號!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,434)\fs21}No Control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們Little Busters目前的活動室就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為棒球社好像出了點糾紛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名義上是廢部狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼選擇棒球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我升上三年級後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直到處求職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其間突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我應該會成為上班族 一直忙於工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這只是因為周邊的人都決定了走這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不經意間隨波逐流了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以為了不間斷地主張自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定開始打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 聽到中途還算明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一句無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要為了自我主張而打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球從哪蹦出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰會在求職期間打棒球?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個的確沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般沒人會有這個打算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這跟我們一毛錢關係都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作為副將 責任也不小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自我主張我選擇揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他去吧 理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總有一天會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我們都還完全沒理解的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1853年佩利 駛入浦賀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你不用做功課的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這不正在做嘛 看就明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來他居然要打棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實讓人始料未及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介就是那種會讓人跌破眼鏡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點地球人都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 又來拉我們打棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 今天有份作業很棘手 幫我一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓收集偉人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偉人的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是名言咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓也會從棍子上摔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}※原句為猴子也會從樹上摔下來 顧名思義是指專業人士也會有失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是名言是諺語吧 而且錯得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新名言誕生於此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.84,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,貓也會從棍子上摔下來 井之原真人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥我也要被叫來男生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒空幫人做作業來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此 我就真心講幾句名言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們看看我「那孩子還有點帥喔」的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這句我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:30.78,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真白癡! 棗鈴(仰視著舊友·井之原真人)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把語境也補上啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短一句就把真人形容透徹了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.92,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子說啥!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嘛 擦 缺幾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一句深奧的名言誕生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:54.60,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嘛 擦 缺幾！ 井之原真人(回顧起其一生)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人生中到底發生什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不會是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你捅了側腹很痛而已啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我把棒球賽的日程都定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是Little Busters的首次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餘下時日不多 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介你聽好 我們還需要以下幾樣東西才能打比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘隊員 練習時間 你以外的隊員的幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剩餘隊員啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙說了兩次剩餘隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人這麼說肯定有他的想法 別追究了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真沒有 對不起了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我摸遍你全身把白癡傳給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘隊員現在開始找就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打棒球最少需要9人啊 還剩5人 找得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說謙吾你把自己除外了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 招集隊員的任務就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招集隊員?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長和陌生人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 耳機?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 鈴!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招集剩下5人 這就是你的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 將鈴派入女生宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把女學生招進Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼選女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是因為男的居多太乏味了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是鈴 成功潛入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先向人打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的女生似乎即使到了下午打招呼也說早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太冗長了 是內行人就應該說早好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪方面的內行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 我發現了一個重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速說一遍「Oliver Sauce」 聽起來很像「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定好了嗎 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oliver Sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那「俺是齊藤」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來有點像「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 是齊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來超像的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像個頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你自己想一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是齊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫齊藤啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是鈴 任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 按常理說晚上好試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 拉她入隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對棒球有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同學有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒不了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒興趣哦 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 棗同學 這是某種新遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對棒球有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…不會不知道本小姐笹瀨川佐佐美是壘球社的下任隊長候補吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你是學園人氣第一的棗恭介學長的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且與劍道社的英雄宮澤同學以及一個肌肉白癡很熟絡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用這麼跩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉白癡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你丫是英雄?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這評價算中肯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴 告訴她宮澤每次泡澡時都穿著衣服 還把襪子套在腦袋上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢罵我蠢蛋!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們三個 給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚 很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐佐美大人 太華麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時起 我們被恭介心血來潮捲了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過恭介本人還是一如既往地抱著漫畫看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那足以引來其他班級女生圍觀的閱讀姿態 該如何形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說神聖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑 氣憤 時而抽泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那一成不變如少年般多彩的表情吸引著旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止都在一起的我們畢業後也可能各奔東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能說的是 一年後恭介肯定不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做只有現在做得到的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我也來試著拉Little Busters的隊員吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時起我也如是決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟最先提出想和大家一起做些什麼的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先打聲招呼再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 世上有很多不可思議的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如甜點和甜點和甜點 所以甜點從天而降了
